boxes-and-lines Pirate Fleet Command

tag Status as s
  Operational green
  Damaged orange
  Sunk red
  Building blue default

active-tag Status

Flagship s: Operational
  -> [Harbor Defenses]
  -> IntelNetwork

[Harbor Defenses]
  FortCannon s: Operational
    -> Watchtower
  Watchtower s: Operational
  SeaMines s: Building

IntelNetwork s: Operational
  -> SpyRing
  -> SignalFlags

SpyRing s: Operational
  -> [Harbor Defenses]

SignalFlags s: Damaged
